                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_a_chatbot.dita" xtrc="p:17;132:24">Now, when you click on <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_a_chatbot.dita" xtrc="b:1;132:50">Intents</b>, the converted questions should
