                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_a_chatbot.dita" xtrc="p:20;142:24"><image href="../images/chatbot-chat-demo.png" id="image_dmf_514_wsb" scale="60" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_a_chatbot.dita" xtrc="image:9;143:41" dita-ot:image-width="498" dita-ot:image-height="663"/></p>
